  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and cook for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and oat milk, bringing the mixture to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add the rolled oats, smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper; stir to combine.",
    "Simmer the soup for 7-8 minutes, or until the oats are tender and the soup thickens to a creamy consistency.",
    "Whisk in the lemon zest and freshly squeezed lemon juice, adjusting salt as needed.",
    "Fold in the nutritional yeast for a richer flavor; stir until well incorporated.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning, adding more pepper or lemon juice if desired.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley."
